[Arch Linux](https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Installation_guide)
  + don't forget to install NetworkManager
[Hyprland](https://wiki.hyprland.org/Getting-Started/Installation/)
  + hyprlock (lock screen)
  + hypridle (idle management)
  + hyprpaper (wallpaper)
  + dunst (notification server)
  + waybar (status bar)
  + firefox + naezr/ShyFox theme
  + dolphin (file manager)
  + spotify + spicetify themes
  + webcord
  + qimgv (image viewer)
  + vlc (video player)
  + noto-fonts (-emoji, -extra) + Source Code Pro font
  + tlp (power saving)

yay -Sy --noconfirm hyprland hyprlock hypridle hyprpaper dunst waybar firefox dolphin spotify webcord qimgv vlc noto-fonts noto-fonts-emoji noto-fonts-extra tlp
